es pain management, symptom control, and emotional support for patients and their families.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-35_ pf-text-1">Palliative care is not limited to end-of-life care; it can begin at diagnosis and continue throughout the treatment process.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-37_ pf-text-1">It addresses physical, emotional, social, and spiritual needs, aiming to improve the overall well-being of patients and families.</li></ul></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-39_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Empowering_Caregivers_Expert-Led_Courses_in_Hospice_and_Palliative_Care_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710854660" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Empowering_Caregivers_Expert-Led_Courses_in_Hospice_and_Palliative_Care_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710854660 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Empowering_Caregivers_Expert-Led_Courses_in_Hospice_and_Palliative_Care_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.jpg?v=1710854660 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Empowering_Caregivers_Expert-Led_Courses_in_Hospice_and_Palliative_Care_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.jpg?v=1710854660 320w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Empowering Caregivers Expert-Led Courses in Hospice and Palliative Care - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Empowering Caregivers Expert-Led Courses in Hospice and Palliative Care - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-40_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-41_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by winnievinzence

