aining_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710854660" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Empowering_Caregivers_Expert-Led_Courses_in_Hospice_and_Palliative_Care_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710854660 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Empowering Caregivers Expert-Led Courses in Hospice and Palliative Care - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Empowering Caregivers Expert-Led Courses in Hospice and Palliative Care - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-120_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-121_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by winnievinzence

 via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-123_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-124_ pf-text-1">Hospice care emphasises comfort and quality of life for patients with terminal illnesses.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-126_ pf-text-1">It often includes pain management, symptom control, and emotional support for patients and their families.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-128_ pf-text-1">Palliative care is not limited to end-of-life care; it can begin at diagnosis and continue throughout the treatment process.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-130_ pf-text-1">It addresses physical, emotional, social, and spiritual needs, aiming to improve the overall well-being of patients and families.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-132_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-133_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-134_ pf-heading-1-h3">The role of World Hospice and Palliative Care Day</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Elevate_Your_Skills_Enroll_Now_for_Compassionate_End-of-Life_Support_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710858918" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Elevate_Your_Skills_Enroll_Now_for_Compassionate_End-of-Life_Support_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710858918 1536w" width="1000" height="697" alt="Elevate Your Skills Enroll Now for Compassionate End-of-Life Support - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Elevate Your Skills Enroll Now for Compassionate End-of-Life Support - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-136_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-137_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by tan4ikk via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-139_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-140_ pf-text-1"><b>Raising awareness</b> - The day serves as a platform to raise awareness about hospice and palliative care services globally.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-142_ pf-text-1"><b>Advocacy</b> - Organisations like the Worldwide Hospice Palliative Care Alliance (WHPCA) and Hospice UK advocate for better policies and resources to support palliative care initiatives.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-144_ pf-text-1"><b>Empowerment</b> - By educating the public about the importance of compassionate end-of-life care, World Hospice and Palliative Care Day empowers patients and families to make informed decisions about their care.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-146_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-147_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-148_ pf-heading-1-h3">Supporting organisations</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/World_Hospice_Day_Training_Programs_Enhance_Your_Expertise_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710859014" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/World_Hospice_Day_Training_Programs_Enhance_Your_Expertise_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710859014 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="World Hospice Day Training Programs Enhance Your Expertise - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -.jpg__PID:63fb83df-a952-4ca4-bcef-ccdcf7f46b15" title="World Hospice Day Training Programs Enhance Your Expertise - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-150_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-151_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by paegagz via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-153_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-154_ pf-text-1"><b>Worldwide</b> - Organisations like the WHO and NHPCO provide guidance and resources to support palliative care initiatives globally.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-156_ pf-text-1"><b>UK-Specific</b> - Hospice UK and Marie Curie offer support and resources for hospices and individuals seeking palliative care services in the UK. Additionally, The Mandatory Training Group, a leading UK provider of World Hospice and Palliative Care Day-related content, offers comprehensive training and educational materials to healthcare professionals and caregivers.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-158_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-159_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-160_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_4479c3e5-312a-4608-a35d-cabc6d2d52c6.jpg?v=1710763593" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_4479c3e5-312a-4608-a35d-cabc6d2d52c6.jpg?v=1710763593 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Expert-Led Courses on Hospice and Palliative Care Principles - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Expert-Led Courses on Hospice and Palliative Care Principles - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-162_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-163_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by mohdizzuanbinroslan via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-165_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-166_ pf-text-1">According to the World Health Organisation (WHO), only about 14% of people who need palliative care currently receive it.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-168_ pf-text-1">Palliative care aims to relieve suffering and improve the quality of life for patients facing life-threatening illnesses and their families.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-170_ pf-text-1">Hospice care focuses on providing comfort and support for terminally ill patients in their final stages of life, often in their own homes or specialised hospice facilities.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-172_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-173_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-174_ pf-heading-1-h3">Recommendations</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Advocate_for_Compassionate_End-of-Life_Care_Enroll_Today_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710859190" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Advocate_for_Compassionate_End-of-Life_Care_Enroll_Today_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710859190 1536w" width="1000" height="605" alt="Advocate for Compassionate End-of-Life Care Enroll Today - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Advocate for Compassionate End-of-Life Care Enroll Today - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-176_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-177_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by SpaceOak via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-179_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-180_ pf-text-1"><b>Educate yourself</b> - Learn about hospice and palliative care and how it can benefit you or your loved ones.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-182_ pf-text-1"><b>Spread awareness</b> - Share information about World Hospice and Palliative Care Day and the importance of compassionate end-of-life care with your community.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-184_ pf-text-1"><b>Support organisations</b> - Consider volunteering or donating to organisations that provide hospice and palliative care services. Explore the training and educational resources offered by The Mandatory Training Group to enhance your knowledge and skills in providing compassionate care.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-186_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-187_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-188_ pf-heading-1-h3">Conclusion</h3><img src="https://cdn.sho